column5: That really sucks. Didn’t think me wanting to have fun with someone made me look like I had no respect for myself. I just wanted to have fun with someone I was attracted to. That really sucks. He probably makes fun of me with his friends. Ugh this really makes me feel like shit.
Honestly wished I was this skinny
Why is it so hard to believe this is a real question? Lol

The only thing I’m worried about is being accused of stealing the deposit that I did not touch. I don’t care about this company anymore. They got rid of 3 manager within a year, and 5 employees. I just don’t want to end up in jail for something I did not do.
